design:
## Goal
Implement hook that analyzes prompts and injects skill activation reminders.

## Effort Estimate
6-8 hours

## Success Criteria
- [ ] UserPromptSubmit hook created and configured in hooks.json
- [ ] Hook analyzes prompts using skill-rules.json patterns
- [ ] Top 3 matching skills injected as additionalContext
- [ ] Priority-based sorting (critical > high > medium > low)
- [ ] Hook handles errors gracefully (always returns decision: continue)
- [ ] Performance: <100ms for typical prompt analysis
- [ ] Manual testing with 5 sample prompts shows correct skill activation
- [ ] Hook doesn't block or crash on malformed input

